f3.jpg" alt="Thomas Elms stars in UBC Theatre&#039;s production of The Seagull. Photo courtesy Tim Matheson." width="540" height="359" class="size-large wp-image-42467" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Thomas Elms stars in UBC Theatre&#8217;s production of The Seagull. Photo courtesy Tim Matheson.</p></div>
